review_blob: Pretty tastie brew. My bubby bought it and didnt like it,And I tried it and Liked it so we traded.  Nothing too fancy, But tastes like it was brewed with love. Nice smooth creamy kinda coffee and vanilla flavours. I am liking it more every sip :D   Very drinkable
Hints of vomit, Musty basement, sour sink sponge, moth balls, battery acid, with a nice urine finish
Deliciousness, floral, citrus, earthy,light sweetness, medium bitterness, medium sourness, thin feel, light body, fizzy,
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - Tank 7 Farmhouse Ale
